# AI Provider Routing Protection

Use `supabase/functions/_shared/ai-utils.ts` as the single routing source.

Must preserve:
- Providers: `openai`, `anthropic`, `google`, `perplexity`.
- Dispatcher usage: `routedChatCompletion(...)` (no direct provider fetches in functions).
- API key lookup order: `integration_settings` then env fallback.
- Defaults:
  - `openai`: `gpt-4o-mini`
  - `google`: `gemini-2.0-flash`
  - `anthropic`: `claude-3-5-haiku-latest`
  - `perplexity`: `llama-3.1-sonar-small-128k-online`
- Google `NOT_FOUND` auto-recovery model discovery/retry.
- Provider-agnostic readiness checks (never OpenAI-only gates).
